io.tarantool.driver.api

Interface CallResult<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - target result type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DDLMetadataContainerResult, MultiValueCallResult<T,R>, SingleValueCallResult<T>, TarantoolIndexMetadataResult, TarantoolSpaceMetadataResult, TarantoolTupleMultiResult, TarantoolTupleSingleResult
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiValueCallResultImpl, SingleValueCallResultImpl

    public interface CallResult<T>
    Basic interface for Tarantool call operation result -- an array of elements corresponding to the Lua multi-return result, usually two values -- an result and a error.
